{"prompt": "Generate a website for a video game studio. The website should be vibrant and use red as the brand color.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Crimson Byte Studios</title>\n    <style>\n        :root {\n            --brand-color: #c0392b;\n            --secondary-color: #e74c3c;\n            --text-color: #ffffff;\n            --bg-color: #1a1a1a;\n        }\n\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            background-color: var(--bg-color);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            line-height: 1.6;\n        }\n\n        header {\n            background: linear-gradient(to right, var(--brand-color), var(--secondary-color));\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            padding: 2rem 0;\n            text-align: center;\n            border-bottom: 4px solid var(--brand-color);\n        }\n\n        header h1 {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-size: 3rem;\n            text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);\n        }\n\n        nav {\n            text-align: center;\n            background-color: #2a2a2a;\n            padding: 1rem 0;\n        }\n\n        nav a {\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            text-decoration: none;\n            margin: 0 15px;\n            font-weight: bold;\n            transition: color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        nav a:hover {\n            color: var(--secondary-color);\n        }\n\n        .container {\n            width: 80%;\n            margin: auto;\n            overflow: hidden;\n            padding: 30px 0;\n        }\n\n        .main-content {\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 40px 0;\n        }\n\n        .main-content h2 {\n            color: var(--brand-color);\n            font-size: 2.5rem;\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n        }\n\n        .game-showcase {\n            display: grid;\n            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));\n            gap: 30px;\n            margin-top: 30px;\n        }\n\n        .game-card {\n            background-color: #2a2a2a;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            overflow: hidden;\n            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);\n            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;\n            border-top: 5px solid var(--brand-color);\n        }\n\n        .game-card:hover {\n            transform: translateY(-5px);\n            box-shadow: 0 8px 16px rgba(0,0,0,0.4);\n        }\n\n        .game-card img {\n            width: 100%;\n            height: 200px;\n            object-fit: cover;\n        }\n\n        .game-card-content {\n            padding: 20px;\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n\n        .game-card-content h3 {\n            margin-top: 0;\n            color: var(--brand-color);\n            font-size: 1.8rem;\n        }\n\n        .game-card-content p {\n            font-size: 0.95rem;\n            color: #ccc;\n        }\n\n        footer {\n            background-color: #111;\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 20px 0;\n            margin-top: 30px;\n            border-top: 2px solid var(--brand-color);\n        }\n\n        footer p {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-size: 0.9rem;\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n    <header>\n        <h1>Crimson Byte Studios</h1>\n    </header>\n\n    <nav>\n        <a href=\"#about\">About Us</a>\n        <a href=\"#games\">Our Games</a>\n        <a href=\"#contact\">Contact</a>\n    </nav>\n\n    <div class=\"container\">\n        <section id=\"about\" class=\"main-content\">\n            <h2>About Crimson Byte</h2>\n            <p>Welcome to Crimson Byte Studios, where passion for gaming meets cutting-edge development. We craft immersive worlds and unforgettable experiences for players around the globe. Our team is dedicated to pushing the boundaries of interactive entertainment, fueled by a love for all things digital.</p>\n        </section>\n\n        <section id=\"games\" class=\"main-content\">\n            <h2>Our Latest Titles</h2>\n            <div class=\"game-showcase\">\n                <div class=\"game-card\">\n                    <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/300x200/c0392b/ffffff?text=Game+Title+1\" alt=\"Game 1 Artwork\">\n                    <div class=\"game-card-content\">\n                        <h3>Shadowfall</h3>\n                        <p>A dark fantasy RPG with branching narratives and intense combat.</p>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"game-card\">\n                    <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/300x200/e74c3c/ffffff?text=Game+Title+2\" alt=\"Game 2 Artwork\">\n                    <div class=\"game-card-content\">\n                        <h3>Cosmic Drift</h3>\n                        <p>Fast-paced arcade racer through procedurally generated nebulae.</p>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"game-card\">\n                    <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/300x200/c0392b/ffffff?text=Game+Title+3\" alt=\"Game 3 Artwork\">\n                    <div class=\"game-card-content\">\n                        <h3>Pixel Purge</h3>\n                        <p>Retro-inspired roguelike with challenging gameplay and charming visuals.</p>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </section>\n\n        <section id=\"contact\" class=\"main-content\">\n            <h2>Get in Touch</h2>\n            <p>Have questions, feedback, or just want to say hello? We'd love to hear from you!</p>\n            <p>Email us at: <a href=\"mailto:info@crimsonbytestudios.com\" style=\"color: var(--secondary-color);\">info@crimsonbytestudios.com</a></p>\n        </section>\n   